{"id":46906,"type":3,"name":"夢みたあとで","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/9a/1b/46906_jp.jpg","rating":{"total":17,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":1,"7":6,"8":4,"9":1,"10":4},"score":7.9},"summary":"柯南 ED14 第266話 - 第287話（計22話）\r\n此曲于2002年3月13日发售。作词AZUKI七、作曲中村由利、编曲古井弘人。《梦醒之后-Gomi's Lair Remix-》混音为DJ GOMI。\r\n\r\n继《Mysterious Eyes》《夏之幻》之后，再次为《名侦探柯南》演唱歌曲。首次进入公信榜前10位。发售枚数打到10万枚以上，是GARNET CROW最大的销售枚数。\r\n\r\n此曲为中村由利首次创作的歌曲。此曲在2001年4月に作为第七张单曲被讨论其发售日期，在同年3月发售中止（却而代之，作为第七张单曲，《Last love song》于5月9日发售）。在此之前，好像被讨论单曲化，不过发表其全部都是虚假，直到2002年3月13日的发售日为止才成真。\r\n\r\n在2002年3月12日的日本电视台‘AX MUSIC FACTORY’中、于3月15日在全国节目朝日电视台《Music Station》中出席演出。这是GARNET CROW第一次上电视节目。\r\n\r\n在三首歌曲中，由DJ GOMI混音的版本，歌曲在最后歌词和原曲有区别。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>梦醒之后</li><li><span>艺术家: </span><a href=\"/person/9957\">GARNET CROW</a></li><li><span>厂牌: </span><a href=\"/person/13308\">GIZA studio</a></li><li><span>录音: </span><a href=\"/person/13308\">GIZA studio</a></li><li><span>版本特性: </span>Single / Maxi</li><li><span>发售日期: </span>2002-03-13</li><li><span>价格: </span>￥ 1,260</li><li><span>播放时长: </span>18 m</li><li><span>发行商: </span>GIZA studio</li>","collection":{"collect":25},"tags":[{"name":"名探偵コナン","count":4},{"name":"GARNET_CROW","count":3},{"name":"2002","count":2},{"name":"ED","count":2},{"name":"anime","count":2},{"name":"名侦探柯南","count":2},{"name":"GARNET.CROW","count":1},{"name":"＊＊＊","count":1},{"name":"single","count":1},{"name":"单曲","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":0,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/0","type":0,"sort":0,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":""}],"disc":[{"title":"Disc 1","disc":[{"title":"1 夢みたあとで","href":"/ep/191389"},{"title":"2 幸福なペット","href":"/ep/191390"},{"title":"3 夢みたあとで-Gomi's Lair Remix-","href":"/ep/191391"},{"title":"4 夢みたあとで-Instrumental-","href":"/ep/191392"}]}],"staff":[{"id":9957,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f6/1a/9957_prsn_73So6.jpg","name":"GARNET CROW","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":13308,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/16/7e/13308_prsn_31AQ